name: AtomsQuiz
0:
”Alexa, quiz me on atoms”
”my answer is 3”
”I don't know”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: quiz me on atoms
des:
This skill is a ten question quiz on atoms. This skill will provide you with a question, and from four given answer choices, select the correct answer to the question by saying "my answer is" and the number of your selected answer choice.
 No additional hardware is required. Initiate this skill by saying "Alexa quiz me on atoms"
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
